  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to KDE-Cli-Tools</title>

    <para>
      The <application>KDE-Cli-Tools</application> package contains
      tools based on KDE Frameworks 5 to better interact with the
      system.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

